run this script to create a bastion host in the public subnet
./env_pub_inst.sh aws_region ami-1234567890abcdefg t2.micro key_name name-of-public-security-group subnet-1234567890abcdefg name-of-instance


run the script to create a instance in private-subnet
./env_prvt_inst.sh aws_region ami-1234567890abcdefg t2.micro key_name name-of-private-security-group subnet-1234567890abcdefg name-of-instance

